227
00:12:09,411 --> 00:12:11,790
Rym: Yeah, the stock skyrocketed on the news.

228
00:12:11,912 --> 00:12:12,809
Rym: Relatively speaking.

229
00:12:12,809 --> 00:12:16,610
Rym: 6%, over 6% in one day is a pretty big skyrocket.

230
00:12:16,890 --> 00:12:23,590
