233
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:47,269
Rym: Yes, that's called insider trading.

234
00:12:47,450 --> 00:12:54,410
Scott: Right, like if you knew for sure that you were part of the layoff making decision, don't buy your own stock because you will go to jail.

235
00:12:54,511 --> 00:13:06,059
Scott: But if you get wind or maybe just a feeling that something bad's going down, buy your own company's stock and then when the SEC comes to ask, be like, "I worked at the company, I wanted to invest in it, it's completely innocent,".

236
00:13:06,301 --> 00:13:12,010
