330
00:19:23,274 --> 00:19:23,363
Scott: Yeah.

331
00:19:23,530 --> 00:19:25,508
Scott: If you swap to other people, then...

332
00:19:25,750 --> 00:19:29,130
Rym: No, you don't know if your role was swapped, so the drunk knows that he swapped with someone else.

333
00:19:29,292 --> 00:19:30,790
Scott: Right, so the drunk knows something.

334
00:19:30,930 --> 00:19:34,990
Scott: The drunk knows that so-and-so was Mafia and the drunk knows so-and-so is now drunk.

335
00:19:35,411 --> 00:19:37,849
